data.description: Welcome to this charming 1950s home nestled in the heart of Griffin. This well maintained property offers a perfect blend of vintage charm and modern comfort. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of hardwood floors that flow seamlessly throughout the home. The spacious living room features large windows, allowing natural light to illuminate the space.    This home offers four generously sized bedrooms, providing plenty of space for the whole family. The original master bedroom, currently used as a living room, offers a private fireplace and en suite.    Step outside to discover your own private oasis. The backyard is perfect for outdoor gatherings, with a charming outdoor fireplace creating a cozy ambiance on cool evenings. The detached garage offers convenient parking and additional storage space. The screened in porch is great place to enjoy your morning coffee.    Located in a desirable neighborhood, this home is just minutes away from parks, schools, shopping, and dining options. Don't miss your opportunity to make this gem your own!
